The Asus Eee PC 1000H was released in September 2008.<br />
Basic features: 10-inch screen, Intel Atom N270, 1GB of RAM (upgradable to 2GB), 160GB Harddisc, 1.3-Megapixel-Webcam, Bluetooth WLAN-N support
= Installation =
== Choosing the right installation medium ==
The Eee PC 1000H does not have an optical drive, like every other Netbook, using a LiveUSB is the common choose. For instructions and further information see [http://www.gentoo.org/doc/en/liveusb.xml Gentoo Linux LiveUSB HOWTO].
Otherwise use a externel optical drive.
To boot from LiveUSB or disc you have to press ESC, when the Eee PC logo is prompted and select the right installation medium.
== Install process ==
After booting a live system follow the [http://www.gentoo.org/doc/en/handbook/handbook-x86.xml Gentoo Linux x86 Handbook]
